scenes.description: Vestia Zeta introduces her birthday merchandise set, giving a brief overview in English and Indonesian.
Zeta showcases the first item: the Angelic Zeta Acrylic Diorama Stand.
Zeta introduces the second item: the Vestia Zeta Haori.
Zeta presents the third item: the 'Uweee' Cap.
Zeta begins showing the fourth item: the Sleepy Cat Zzz Plushie.
